- Variant located in DNase I hypersensitive site + active enhancer chromatin (H3K27ac+) in vascular tissues
- deCODE pQTL + GTEx eQTL evidence confirms regulatory effect
- Koehler 2020 monogenic phenotype provides orthogonal functional validation
